	* Add dummy variable in sdpa_io.cpp to workaround gcc-3.3
	optimization bug.
        * Parameters are now accord with the manual.
            PARAMETER_AGGRESSIVE -> PARAMETER_UNSTABLE_BUT_FAST
	    PARAMETER_STABLE -> PARAMETER_STABLE_BUT_SLOW
	
